row.Title: The Rams Won’t Get As Much From LA As The Lakers And Dodgers Do FiveThirtyEight
row.Selection: After years of speculation over which NFL team would be the first to surrender to Hollywood’s siren call, the inevitable finally happened: The league’s owners voted this week to allow the Rams to move from St. Louis to Los Angeles.
